<L>__{exterior cedar rapids park day (a little while later)}
<A>__{tim and joan swing on a swing set in a dreary little park overlooking the cedar river. it is a cold, gray day.}
<C>__{tim}
<D>__{he didn't have to yell at me. i didn't do anything wrong. i'm trying my hardest.}
