<D>__{he had just opened northlands. anyway, i remember thinking, this guy's a hero. a real hero. so even if he doesn't always treat me, like y'know... whatever now i will never forget that.}
<A>__{tim jumps off the swing, taking care not to slip in the snow. joan jumps off. they walk toward the river, silent for a bit.}
