<D>__{people talk about the firemen and policemen and that. but think about all the claims in a disaster like that how hard those agents worked to make sure people's lives weren't left in the lurch. we're talking billions of dollars in damages, literally. and claim by claim, dream by dream, those agents helped rebuild this city. i'm telling you, it's a noble calling. i really believe that.}
